MLEA TP 2 - d-hall_f

Classification:

make

or:

python classification.py <filename> <positive label> <data_size> [--noshow]

Note: figures are generated, saved, then displayed.
      to prevent pylab from displaying images, use --noshow
      as the last parameter (all previous parameters are mandatory).


Data sets:

A] Donut:

python donut.py <samples> <noise> <name> [--noshow]

e.g.:
	python donut.py 500 0.2 donut_noisy

Note: See top of file to play with extra parameters

B] Mushroom

python mushroom.py <name> [--noshow]

e.g.:
	python mushroom.py mushroom_data

C] Iris

python iris.py <name> [--noshow]

e.g.:
	python iris.py iris_data


D] Digits

python optdigits.py <name> [--noshow]

e.g.:
	python optdigits.py optdigits_data_tes

_tes: test data
_tra: training data
(in the original dataset)
